---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Apps | DK App Tools"
  description="Apps created by DK App Tools."
>
  <section class="section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Apps</p>
    <h1>Focused tools, built one at a time.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      DK App Tools apps are designed around practical use, clear behavior, and
      respect for the user.
    </p>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Offline FileSecure</h3>
        <p>
          A local-first file vault for Android. No account. No cloud upload. No ads.
          Files added to the vault are stored encrypted on your device.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="button" href="/apps/offline-filesecure">View app</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>More apps coming later</h3>
        <p>
          Future DK App Tools products will follow the same principle: practical,
          focused, and easy to understand.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
